lead_paragraph: Winger Andros Townsend says his main focus now is to keep struggling Newcastle United in the Premier League even if he hopes the move from Tottenham Hotspur also helps him back into the England squad.

headline.print_headline: Townsend Says Newcastle Are His Main Focus Now
